1. INDEPENDENT PROJECT
This repository (ivxv-build) is an independent effort to document and test 
the Estonian E-voting system (IVXV). It is not affiliated with the 
Estonian State Electoral Office (Riigi Valimisteenistus) or RIA.

2. EXTERNAL SOFTWARE (IVXV)
This repository does NOT contain the IVXV source code. 
Official IVXV code is fetched from: https://github.com/valimised/ivxv
IVXV is licensed under: Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivs 3.0 Unported (CC BY-NC-ND 3.0).
Users of this build-tool must comply with the IVXV license terms.

3. TEST DATA AND PRIVACY (GDPR)
This repository contains digital signature containers (.asice / .bdoc) 
provided by project contributors for research and audit purposes.
- These files contain real names and Estonian personal identification 
  codes (isikukood) of the contributors.
- All contributors have explicitly consented to the inclusion of their 
  test-signatures in this public repository to aid the transparency 
  of the e-voting audit process.
- These data are provided "as is" for technical verification only.

4. LICENSE FOR THIS REPOSITORY
The build scripts, Makefiles, and documentation created by the 
ivxv-build project are dedicated to the public domain under the 
Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal license.